StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [sp_GetDutyPreferences]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@ProgramType varchar(4) AS
SELECT P.DUTY_PREFERENCE_CODE, D.DUTY_PREFERENCE_DESCRIPTION FROM PROGRAM_DUTY_PREFERENCE P INNER JOIN DUTY_PREFERENCE D ON P.DUTY_PREFERENCE_CODE = D.DUTY_PREFERENCE_CODE WHERE P.PROGRAM_CODE = @ProgramType ORDER BY D.DUTY_PREFERENCE_DESCRIPTION
